# Serial Command Interface

## Objective
Control LEDs using commands entered through the Serial Monitor.

## Components
- Arduino UNO
- 2 LEDs
- 2 Resistors
- Breadboard

## Supported Commands
- RED ON
- RED OFF
- GREEN ON
- GREEN OFF
- ALL OFF
- STATUS
- HELP

## Concepts Used
- Serial Communication
- String Processing
- Conditional Statements
- Human Machine Interface
